article_title: Master’s Peace Clinic of Hope grand opening Thursday
article_text:
Salem, MO (65560)

Today

Showers and thunderstorms.

Tonight

Thunderstorms likely. A few storms may be severe. Low near 65F. Winds S at 5 to 10 mph. Chance of rain 90%.

article_metadata.author: Tyler McConnell

og.description: Family nurse practitioner Kim Kemnitzer’s decade-long dream of opening a clinic for the homeless, working poor and the uninsured in Dent County is now a reality, and Master’s Peace Clinic
